---
import WorkDetail from '../../layouts/WorkDetail.astro';
---
<WorkDetail
  title="FullFill"
  company="Tashi"
  period="2021 – 2022"
  role="QA Analyst"
  category="Health & Wellness · iOS & Android"
  stack={["React Native", "QA", "iOS & Android"]}
>

  <div class="mb-10">
    <p class="font-mono text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase text-[#c9873a] mb-4">Overview</p>
    <p class="text-[15px] leading-[1.9] text-white/60 font-light">FullFill is a health and wellness app built with React Native for iOS and Android. The app is designed to help users build meaningful habits and track their wellness journey in a structured, motivating way.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-10">
    <p class="font-mono text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase text-[#c9873a] mb-4">My Role</p>
    <p class="text-[15px] leading-[1.9] text-white/60 font-light mb-4">As a QA Analyst at Tashi, I was responsible for the full test process — making sure every release was organized, trackable, and met quality standards before reaching users.</p>
    <div class="space-y-3 mt-4">
      <div class="flex gap-4"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-[#c9873a] flex-shrink-0 mt-2"></span><p class="text-sm text-white/50 font-light leading-relaxed">Organized and managed test processes across development and release cycles.</p></div>
      <div class="flex gap-4"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-[#c9873a] flex-shrink-0 mt-2"></span><p class="text-sm text-white/50 font-light leading-relaxed">Kept track of test cases, results, and defects to ensure full visibility across the team.</p></div>
      <div class="flex gap-4"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-[#c9873a] flex-shrink-0 mt-2"></span><p class="text-sm text-white/50 font-light leading-relaxed">Worked closely with developers to identify, report, and verify bug fixes before release.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>

</WorkDetail>